OL,6,FThe father of the Georgia school
OL,7,Fshooting suspect has been arrested and
OL,8,Fcharged with two counts of second-
OL,9,Fdegree murder.
OL,11,FColin Gray is also accused of four
OL,12,Fcounts of involuntary manslaughter and
OL,13,Feight counts of cruelty to children.
OL,15,FThe charges are in relation to
OL,16,Fallowing his son, Colt Gray, to
OL,17,Fpossess a weapon.
