OL,3,CFather of US school shooting suspect
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FTwo 14-year-old students, Mason
OL,7,FSchermerhorn and Christian Angulo,
OL,8,Falong with maths teachers Richard
OL,9,FAspinwall, 39, and Christina Irimie,
OL,10,F53, were killed at Apalachee High
OL,11,FSchool in Winder, Georgia, on
OL,12,FWednesday morning.
OL,14,FColt Gray has been charged as an adult
OL,15,Fwith four counts of murder after
OL,16,Finvestigators said he fired an AR-15-
OL,17,Fstyle rifle at the school.
