OL,6,FAt least nine others, including eight
OL,7,Fstudents and one teacher, were taken
OL,8,Fto hospital with injuries - seven of
OL,9,Fthem were shot but are all expected to
OL,10,Fsurvive, Georgia Bureau of
OL,11,FInvestigation (GBI) director, Chris
OL,12,FHosey said.
OL,14,FColt will remain in detention after
OL,15,Fappearing at the Barrow County
OL,16,Fcourthouse on Friday, similarly, his
OL,17,Ffather remains jailed without bail.
OL,19,FThe maximum penalty Colt will face is
OL,20,Fa life sentence without parole.
