OL,6,FIn May 2023, Colt was interviewed by
OL,7,Flaw enforcement after receiving
OL,8,Fanonymous tips about online threats to
OL,9,Fcarry out a school shooting, FBI
OL,10,FAtlanta said.
OL,12,FThe FBI narrowed the threats down and
OL,13,Fthe sheriff's office interviewed the
OL,14,Fthen-13-year-old and Colin Gray, who
OL,15,Fsaid there were hunting guns in the
OL,16,Fhouse but the teen did not have
OL,17,Funsupervised access to them. The teen
OL,18,Fdenied making any online threats.
